data.name: cboEmergency_add.UserSQL
data.value: SELECT NULL ,'' ,0 FROM SYS.DUAL UNION SELECT A.CODE , A.CODE_NAME , 1 FROM BAS0102 A WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = FN_ADM_LOAD_HOSP_CODE() AND A.CODE_TYPE = 'EMERGENCY_GUBUN' ORDER BY 3, 1

data.name: grdINP1003.QuerySQL
data.value: SELECT A.RESER_DATE , A.BUNHO , B.SUNAME , A.GWA , FN_BAS_LOAD_GWA_NAME(A.GWA, A.RESER_DATE) GWA_NAME , A.DOCTOR , FN_BAS_LOAD_DOCTOR_NAME(A.DOCTOR, A.RESER_DATE) DOCTOR_NAME , A.TEL1 , A.TEL2 , A.RESER_FKINP1001 , A.PKINP1003 , A.REMARK , A.IPWON_MOKJUK , A.IPWONSI_ORDER_YN , A.SANG_BIGO , A.JISI_DOCTOR , FN_BAS_LOAD_DOCTOR_NAME(A.JISI_DOCTOR, A.RESER_DATE) DOCTOR_NAME , B.SEX , A.HO_DONG , FN_BAS_LOAD_HO_DONG_NAME(A.HO_DONG, A.RESER_DATE) HO_DONG_NAME , A.HO_CODE , A.BED_NO , 'Y' RESER_YN , (SELECT 'Y' FROM DUAL WHERE EXISTS( SELECT 'X' FROM DOC1001 Z WHERE Z.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND Z.FKINP1001 = A.RESER_FKINP1001 AND Z.CERT_JNCD = '010')) DOC_YN , A.EMERGENCY_GUBUN , A.EMERGENCY_DETAIL FROM OUT0101 B , INP1003 A WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND A.BUNHO = :f_bunho AND A.RESER_END_TYPE = '0' /* 예약중 */ AND B.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND B.BUNHO = A.BUNHO ORDER BY A.RESER_DATE DESC

data.name: layBunhoValidation.QuerySQL
data.value: SELECT A.SUNAME , A.TEL , A.TEL , NVL(A.DELETE_YN, 'N') , NVL(A.JUBSU_BREAK, 'N') , B.CODE_NAME JUBSU_BREAK_REASON , A.SEX , '0' FROM BAS0102 B , OUT0101 A WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND A.BUNHO = :f_bunho AND NVL(A.DELETE_YN, 'N') = 'N' AND B.HOSP_CODE(+) = A.HOSP_CODE AND B.CODE_TYPE(+) = 'JUBSU_BREAKE_REASON' AND B.CODE(+) = A.JUBSU_BREAK_REASON
